title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Zim/Leber/Hebert/Korzo/Stef
description: Bruce Boudreau starts the show, Zimmer's weekly X's & O's chat, Leber in studio, Bobby Hebert on Vikes/Saints, Korzo in studio & Kevin Stefanski to close. Celebrating the Gophers and looking ahead to the Vikings in New Orleans!
